'''Chancellor Palpatine Spaceport''' was a [[Spaceport/Legends|facility]] built on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] during the first ten years of [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] chancellorship. When it was connected to the [[Chancellor Palpatine Commercial Nexus]], it became Coruscant's primary [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]], taking over that position from the older [[Galactic City Spaceport]].

Immediately after [[Operation: Knightfall/Legends|Operation: Knightfall]] was put in action, all major skybridges on approach from the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]] were cordoned off and checkpoints were established in order to prevent [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] from reaching a way off of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]].

